        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 794e142c-2f4c-4dcb-a24a-8f0a5280ac72).Image",
        "Description": "Listen up 47. There are two pair of pairs. Lindsey and Grace are together and they are plotting against Jude and Arnold - another pair of lovers, and vice versa. They want to eliminate each other. There cannot be 2 winners in this situation. To keep the peace at the event eliminate all four of them. You are disguised as friend of Lindsey. Good luck 47.",
